featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Ne aradigimizi bilmedigimiz surece magazaya girmemize izin vermezler. "Sadece etrafa bakmamiz icin" iceri girmemize izin vermiyorlardi. Iddia ettikleri sebep? Personel sayisinin az olmasi. 6 ay onceki bir incelemede, sahibinin sorunlari nedeniyle yetersiz personel bulundugunu iddia etmesi de komik. Ugrunda calismak bir kabus olmali cunku bir musteri olarak kapidan iceri girmeme bile izin verilmemesinin bir kabus oldugunu biliyorum. Esimin dogum gunu icin burayi kontrol etmek icin bir saatten fazla surduk!

Eger goz atamazsak ne istedigimizi nasil bilecegiz?

Neredeyse ayrimciliga ugradigimi hissediyorum ve bunu hayatimda bir kez bile iddia etmedim. Birkac dakika once oradaydik ama caddenin karsisindaki benzin istasyonundaki tuvaleti kullanmak icin ayrildik. Nazik bayan, ilk kez "sadece etrafa bakmak icin" girdigimizde bize herhangi bir sorun cikarmadi, ama beyaz erkek sahibi? Tuvaleti kullanmak icin ciktim! Ve 5 dakika oncesinden su ana kadar birdenbire, iceri girmeme izin vermeyecek kadar az personel mi kaldiniz? Otoparkin bu fotografina bakin. Burada kimse yok!

featured_reviews.review_id:
For a minute there this place was really looking on the up and up. Not sure what happened but it seemed plateaued and now they are slowly digging the whole back down into the cringe factory.
This place gets robbed constantly, the employees are not safe, they can't keep the customers safe, so it's a crapshoot every time you go through the door.
Both management and employees are a revolving door of the new characters so you just never know what you're going to get. Prices are extraordinarily in the very high range compared to what they are purchased for.
You can go to Williams trading university online and check the prices of items at cost versus what they are in the store and I will give you an idea of how much money the store makes.
With that much money you would think they would invest back into the store you know at least getting carpets that don't stick to your shoes or a brightly lit exterior to ward off would be thieves.
The point is there are several adult novelty shops in the area if you're looking for head shop items and paraphernalia they do have them here but again they're on the more expensive end of the scale if you're looking for marital aid and adult novelties you can find those here too again check prices.
So, the one thing I will say that this store does have a better variety of clothing items than any other place for dancers in the area. They have a plus size section and an amazing shoe section. When it comes to the gag gifts and bachelorette or bachelor party supplies be sure to check the expiration date. I cannot stress that enough. Many of these items have been there as long as the store has been there so do your due diligence and check before you buy.
Oh and if you're thinking of shoplifting keep in mind that all employees here are given carte blanche to handle the situation however they feel is justifiable. So if somebody's carrying a gun, taser, or other form of protection, they do not apply the same rules that you would find at someplace like Walmart or spencers gifts. I promise you it is not worth the risk.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Bir dakikaligina burasi gercekten yukari ve yukariya bakiyordu. Ne oldugundan emin degilim ama duragan gorunuyordu ve simdi yavas yavas hepsini yalama fabrikasina kaziyorlar.
Burasi surekli soyuluyor, calisanlar guvende degil, musterileri guvende tutamiyorlar, bu yuzden kapidan her girdiginizde bir sacmalik oluyor.
Hem yonetim hem de calisanlar yeni karakterlerin doner kapisidir, dolayisiyla ne elde edeceginizi asla bilemezsiniz. Fiyatlar, satin alindigi fiyatla karsilastirildiginda olaganustu derecede yuksek araliktadir.
Cevrimici olarak Williams Ticaret Universitesi'ne gidebilir ve ogelerin maliyet fiyatlarini magazadakilerle karsilastirabilirsiniz; ben de size magazanin ne kadar para kazandigina dair bir fikir verecegim.
Bu kadar parayla, en azindan ayakkabilariniza yapismayan halilar veya korunmak icin parlak bir dis cepheye sahip olmanin hirsiz olacagini bildiginiz magazaya geri yatirim yapacaklarini dusunursunuz.
Mesele su ki, eger kafa dukkani esyalari ve gerecler ariyorsaniz, burada varlar, ancak evlilik yardimi ariyorsaniz yine olcegin daha pahali ucundalar. Yetiskinlere yonelik yenilikleri burada da bulabilirsiniz, yine fiyatlari kontrol edin.
Bu yuzden soyleyecegim tek sey, bu magazanin bolgedeki danscilar icin diger yerlerden cok daha cesitli giyim esyalarina sahip oldugudur. Buyuk beden bolumu ve harika bir ayakkabi bolumu var. Saka hediyeleri ve bekarliga veda veya bekarliga veda partisi malzemelerine gelince, son kullanma tarihini kontrol ettiginizden emin olun. Bunu yeterince vurgulayamam. Bu ogelerin cogu, magaza orada oldugu surece oradaydi, bu nedenle satin almadan once gerekli ozeni gosterin ve kontrol edin.
Ah, eger magazadan hirsizlik yapmayi dusunuyorsaniz, buradaki tum calisanlara durumu nasil hakli goruyorlarsa oyle halletmeleri icin tam yetki verildigini unutmayin. Yani birisi silah, sok tabancasi veya baska bir koruma tasiyorsa, Walmart veya Spencer'in hediyeleri gibi yerlerde bulacaginiz kurallarin aynisini uygulamaz. Sana soz veriyorum bu riske degmez.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: One cikan kaba bir kiz tarafindan iceri girdigim an aceleye getirildi. Is arkadasi bana yaklasti ve satin almami bulmama yardim etti, o da bana secenekleri gosteriyordu ve ben de istedigimi bulmaya cok yaklasmistim.. kaba genc bayan konusmaya dahil oldu ve bana bir sey almam ve yakin oldugu icin disari cikmam icin baski yapmaya calisti gece yarisina kadar ve sanirim yapacak baska isleri vardi. Ona bana bir saniye vermesini soyledim ve "satisi mi kacirmaya calisiyorsun?" dedim. Demek istedigim, 70 dolarlik bir satis bir seydir.. ve kiz "Bir satisi kaybedecegim.." diye cevap verdi ve ben omuz silktim ve o kaba satici yolu gosterirken uzgun bir sekilde disari ciktim.. ilk seferinde kaba davrandigi icin ozur dilemeye calisti. Iceri girdigimde ama birine yuk gibi davrandiginda bunun hicbir anlami yok. Eger musterilere boyle davraniyorsaniz parami baska bir yere gotursem iyi olur. Disari cikmadan once genc bayanin adini almaya calistim ve beni gormezden geldi, sanirim basinin belaya girmesini istemiyor. Umarim isinizde her sey yolundadir, boyle bir calisanla fiziksel magazanizi kapatip cevrimici satis yapmaya devam etseniz iyi olur.

featured_reviews.review_id:
This used to be my favorite place to go. Nearly every weekend, for months, I visited the place and had a great time. I don't even live near this store, and there were other spots I could be visiting, but I came to Intimate Boutique due to the friendly staff and how open-minded they were. I experienced no judgement or prejudice from them. The staff a year ago was friendly and knowledgeable, and I even volunteered to keep the back clean. I would even meet with an overnight employee at the back and do fun things while managing to keep an eye on the store.
I don't know when this new bunch of employees  got hired, but it seems like they took with them some new rules of their own, and some backwoods attitude you usually found from rude employees from other similar places. They now watch you like a criminal when shopping. If you didn't look very masculine for a guy, they looked at you in a manner that made me feel uncomfortable. The night time shift would smoke weed in the back and although it's none of my business what they do for recreation, I still think this behavior affected the way they conducted business. They now only allow certain working women at the back and it seems like all they do is ask for money in exchange for certain favors. And those who go there to enjoy a private time for themselves are now constantly harassed by peeping toms probably paid under the table by these new employees to find an excuse to get rid of us. I would keep my doors locked because there are several notable shady activities in which I do not want any involvement, not even to witness.
I did have a feeling that it was only a matter of time until something good would eventually spoil. This is no longer the Intimate Boutique where I felt safe and welcomed like those days when they just opened. Settling for another place less like it became a more favorable option, and that should say a lot.
Now to be fair, they have a great selection of merchandise and they are fairly priced for patrons that are considerably caucasian and straight. Make it obvious to the staff working in the evening or overnight that you're anything other than the two aforementioned criteria above, or look remotely less masculine, your shopping experience at Walmart would offer much more convenience than this place.
Oh, they also have a sign on their door that says "women must leave their purse in their vehicle"...? The day men can leave their swollen members and prejudice ego in theirs, maybe the day I consider leaving my bag in my car while parked in a shady parking lot full of cars with prying eyes waiting to rob the contents of any unattended vehicles. I don't experience this type of stupidity elsewhere.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Burasi benim gitmeyi en cok sevdigim yerdi. Aylar boyunca neredeyse her hafta sonu burayi ziyaret ettim ve harika vakit gecirdim. Bu magazanin yakininda bile oturmuyorum ve ziyaret edebilecegim baska yerler de vardi, ancak guler yuzlu personeli ve ne kadar acik fikirli olduklari nedeniyle Intimate Boutique'e geldim. Onlardan herhangi bir yargilama veya onyargi yasamadim. Bir yil once personel dost canlisi ve bilgiliydi, hatta ben arka tarafi temiz tutmaya bile gonullu oldum. Hatta arka tarafta bir gece calisaniyla bulusup eglenceli seyler yaparken bir yandan da magazayi gozetliyordum.
Bu yeni calisan grubunun ne zaman ise alindigini bilmiyorum ama gorunuse gore kendilerine ait bazi yeni kurallari ve diger benzer yerlerdeki kaba calisanlardan gordugunuz bazi tasra tavirlarini da beraberlerinde getirmisler. Artik alisveris yaparken sizi bir suclu gibi izliyorlar. Eger bir erkege gore pek erkeksi gorunmuyorsan, sana beni rahatsiz edecek sekilde bakiyorlardi. Gece vardiyasi arkada ot tuttururdu ve eglence icin ne yaptiklari beni ilgilendirmese de, bu davranisin is yapma sekillerini etkiledigini dusunuyorum. Artik sadece belirli calisan kadinlarin arka planda kalmasina izin veriyorlar ve gorunen o ki tek yaptiklari, bazi iyilikler karsiliginda para istemek. Ve oraya kendilerine ozel vakit gecirmek icin gidenler, artik bizden kurtulmak icin bir bahane bulmak amaciyla muhtemelen bu yeni calisanlar tarafindan masanin altindan odenen gozetleme tomlari tarafindan surekli taciz ediliyor. Kapilarimi kilitli tutardim cunku dahil olmayi, tanik olmayi bile istemedigim birkac onemli karanlik faaliyet var.
Iyi bir seyin eninde sonunda bozulmasinin an meselesi olduguna dair bir his vardi icimde. Burasi artik yeni acildigi gunlerdeki gibi kendimi guvende hissettigim ve hos karsilandigim Intimate Boutique degil. Daha az baska bir yere yerlesmek daha avantajli bir secenek haline geldi ve bu cok sey ifade etmeli.
Adil olmak gerekirse, harika bir urun yelpazesine sahipler ve oldukca beyaz ve heteroseksuel musteriler icin oldukca uygun fiyatlara sahipler. Aksam veya gece calisan personele yukarida belirtilen iki kriterin disinda oldugunuzu veya biraz daha az erkeksi gorundugunuzu acikca belirtin; Walmart'taki alisveris deneyiminiz buradan cok daha fazla kolaylik saglayacaktir.
Ah, bir de kapilarinda "kadinlar cantalarini arabalarinda birakmali" diye bir tabela var... Erkeklerin sismis organlarini ve onyargili egolarini kendi arabalarinda birakabilecekleri gun, belki de cantami arabamda birakmayi dusunecegim gun. Arabayi, merakli gozlerle, sahipsiz araclarin icindekileri calmak icin bekleyen arabalarla dolu golgeli bir otoparka park ederken, bu tur bir aptalligi baska yerde yasamiyorum.

featured_reviews.review_id:
I really wanted to like this place, but today's experience has made me not want to come back.

I was greeted by the staff when I first came in and they asked me if I needed any help. I explained to them that I was looking for an outfit to wear to an EDM show and started browsing around in the first floor. After picking out a couple of things, I went to the second floor to browse around and noticed that one of the employees had followed behind me. They went back downstairs to pick up a call and I kept browsing around. However, when I turned around to go back downstairs I noticed that the same employee that had initially followed behind me was staring at me from the middle of the stairs. It made me feel a bit uncomfortable that I was being watched, but assumed it was the store protocol. (This made me uncomfortable because it's never happened to me before and I was the only customer in the store at the time)

When I went downstairs, to try on the outfits I had picked out, the two employees started talking loudly about how they didn't like certain EDM genres (which is okay) and one of them mentioned that their boyfriend thought that electronic music was "trash" (again, personal opinions are okay) and how they didn't like going to festivals because they were packed and full of people on drugs. The whole conversation made me a bit uncomfortable since they weren't talking about that until I was within hearing distance and also found it a bit ironic since the store advertises itself as "Houston's biggest festival superstore"

Overall the store had a lot of cute things and I would have loved to come back for Halloween costume shopping if it wasn't for this experience.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Burayi gercekten sevmek istedim ama bugunku deneyim beni geri gelmek istememe neden oldu.

Ilk geldigimde personel tarafindan karsilandim ve yardima ihtiyacim olup olmadigini sordular. Onlara bir EDM sovunda giymek icin bir kiyafet aradigimi soyledim ve birinci katta dolasmaya basladim. Birkac sey sectikten sonra etrafa goz atmak icin ikinci kata ciktim ve calisanlardan birinin arkamdan geldigini fark ettim. Bir cagriyi almak icin alt kata geri donduler ve ben de etrafa goz atmaya devam ettim. Ancak asagi inmek icin arkami dondugumde, ilk basta arkamdan gelen ayni calisanin merdivenlerin ortasindan bana baktigini fark ettim. Izleniyor olmam beni biraz rahatsiz etti ama bunun magaza protokolu oldugunu varsaydim. (Bu beni rahatsiz etti cunku daha once hic basima gelmemisti ve o sirada magazadaki tek musteri bendim)

Sectigim kiyafetleri denemek icin asagi indigimde, iki calisan yuksek sesle belirli EDM turlerini sevmediklerinden bahsetmeye basladilar (ki bu sorun degil) ve iclerinden biri erkek arkadasinin elektronik muzigi " cop" (yine, kisisel gorusler sorun degil) ve uyusturucu bagimlisi insanlarla dolu ve tika basa dolu olduklari icin festivallere gitmeyi nasil sevmediklerini. Tum konusma beni biraz rahatsiz etti cunku ben duyma mesafesine gelene kadar bundan bahsetmediler ve ayrica magaza kendisini "Houston'in en buyuk festival magazasi" olarak tanittigi icin bunu biraz ironik buldular.

Genel olarak magazada pek cok sevimli sey vardi ve bu deneyim olmasaydi Cadilar Bayrami kostumu alisverisi icin geri gelmeyi cok isterdim.
featured_reviews.response_from_owner_translated_text:
Merhaba Karen! Buradaki deneyiminiz oldugu icin uzgunum. Dikkatimize sundugunuz icin tesekkur ederiz. Sizi temin ederim ki bu calisan artik burada calismiyor.
Umarim bir dahaki gelisinizde daha keyifli bir deneyim yasarsiniz. <3

featured_reviews.review_id:
Lingerie Gifts is one of the smaller adult sex stores (aka: book stores) in the area, but that's not necessarily a bad thing. The stand alone building features a private (though not necessarily secluded) parking lot, a retail specialty area (the front portion, with windows facing the parking lot, is closed off and not  utilised), and an adult arcade.

The parking lot is lit well enough, and I feel safe for the most part. I've never had any problems there. For those so inclined, it's a rather cruisey energy w,,ith an abundance of hideaway spots for added convenience.

The arcade is pretty chill with a good, mixed crowd and a fairly steady stream of people.  There's about 12-15 private rooms, each with a bench, trash can, and a television with controls to change both the volume and the channel . Movies are switched out pretty regularly and there's usually several really good ones. No "theatre" or "couples" area, but there is a bathroom and a staging area, lol.

Cost to get in is $6 (via bill acceptor next to door to area. Cashier can accept $6 via credit card. The arcade is definitely frequented mostly by gay, bi, and/or questioning men of the Hispanic background. On the rare occasion, a chick may find her way back there.

Do I recommend? Yes.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Lingerie Gifts bolgedeki daha kucuk yetiskin seks magazalarindan biridir (diger adiyla: kitapcilar), ancak bu mutlaka kotu bir sey degildir. Mustakil binada ozel (her ne kadar tenha olmasa da) bir otopark, bir perakende uzmanlik alani (pencereleri otoparka bakan on kisim kapalidir ve kullanilmamaktadir) ve yetiskinlere yonelik bir oyun salonu bulunmaktadir.

Otopark yeterince iyi aydinlatiliyor ve cogunlukla kendimi guvende hissediyorum. Orada hic sorun yasamadim. Bu kadar istekli olanlar icin, daha fazla rahatlik icin bol miktarda saklanma noktasiyla birlikte oldukca hareketli bir enerjidir.

Atari salonu, iyi, karisik bir kalabalik ve oldukca istikrarli bir insan akisiyla oldukca sakin. Yaklasik 12-15 ozel oda var, her birinde bir bank, cop kutusu ve hem ses seviyesini hem de kanali degistirmeye yarayan kontrollere sahip bir televizyon var. Filmler oldukca duzenli olarak degistiriliyor ve genellikle birkac gercekten iyi film var. "Tiyatro" ya da "ciftler" alani yok ama banyo ve sahneleme alani var, hahaha.

Iceri girmenin maliyeti 6 dolardir (yan taraftaki fatura kabul eden kisi araciligiyla. Kasiyer kredi kartiyla 6 dolar kabul edebilir. Oyun salonuna kesinlikle cogunlukla gey, biseksuel ve/veya Ispanyol kokenli sorgulayici erkekler ugrar. Nadiren de olsa, bir pilic oraya donus yolunu bulabilir.

Tavsiye eder miyim? Evet.

(Orijinal)
No never is. Some items u can find cheaper but most items are abt the same price elsewhere. I think they have more women's lingerie than any other places near by, hardly any clothing for guys.  As far as employees, there is 2 that are polite, friendly & go out of their way to help. There's only 1 female that works there and I rather go when she's working than one of the other ones.

featured_reviews.review_id:
On 10/22/22 at 5:33pm (the time on the receipt is incorrect) my husband and I visited this store. There were two young women working at the store at the time. They were not very friendly. One women, a tall women dressed in a sorceress costume, was condescending at times. We were not greeted when we entered the store but I was immediately told to put my bag in the locker which I thought was odd. My husband asked her the same question about a product and she ignored him 3 times. It got so bad that I had to tell her to answer his question. They had a lot of knowledge about products but they weren't personable and I didn't feel comfortable talking to them.

My husband, being the kind soul that he is, even tipped them--they didn't even bother to say "Thank you." During checkout, I wasn't thanked for my business. I got the impression that my business was unappreciated and that I was bothering them.

22.10.22 tarihinde saat 17:33'te (makbuzdaki saat yanlis) kocam ve ben bu magazayi ziyaret ettik. O sirada magazada iki genc kadin calisiyordu. Pek arkadas canlisi degillerdi. Buyucu kostumu giymis uzun boylu bir kadin, zaman zaman kucumseyici davraniyordu. Magazaya girdigimizde karsilanmadik ama hemen cantami garip oldugunu dusundugum dolaba koymam soylendi. Kocam ona bir urunle ilgili ayni soruyu sordu ve o onu 3 kez gormezden geldi. O kadar kotulesti ki, sorusuna cevap vermesini soylemek zorunda kaldim. Urunler hakkinda cok bilgileri vardi ama cana yakin degillerdi ve onlarla konusurken kendimi rahat hissetmiyordum.

Kocam iyi kalpli biri oldugundan onlara bahsis bile verdi; onlar "Tesekkur ederim" deme zahmetine bile girmediler. Odeme sirasinda isim icin tesekkur edilmedi. Yaptigim isin takdir edilmedigi ve onlari rahatsiz ettigim izlenimine kapildim.

featured_reviews.review_id:
The store has a decent selection and at first I was excited to find the location, but Customer service after the transaction is complete is seriously lacking. Less than 24 hours ago I purchased a pair of Ellie shoes on clearance. As an entertainer, a pair of shoes for work at a discount is a score but still not cheap. Today I took them out of the box for a test run before work but the buckle was broken. I immediately took a picture and messaged the store on Facebook. After no response I gave them a call and they refuse to so much as exchange them for another pair of clearance shoes. So now I'm stuck with a pair of $60 stripper heels that are broken.
Previously, another adult boutique sold me a pair of shoes by the same brand that literally fell apart after my first shift, but they went out of their way to contact their vendor and replace my shoes when I told them what happened.
I understand what kind of store it is and I get the return policies are in place for a reason but I'm not returning a used vibrator or asking for some thing of higher value. I just think the right thing to do customer service-wise would be to give store credit or a refund. We pump so much money into our wardrobe at adult boutiques it would've went right back to Cindie's anyways.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Magazanin iyi bir secimi var ve ilk basta yeri bulmak beni heyecanlandirdi, ancak islem tamamlandiktan sonra musteri hizmetleri ciddi sekilde eksik. 24 saatten kisa bir sure once indirimli olarak bir cift Ellie ayakkabisi satin aldim. Bir sovmen olarak, is icin indirimli bir cift ayakkabi bir puandir, ancak yine de ucuz degildir. Bugun ise gitmeden once deneme amacli olarak kutusundan cikardim ancak tokasi kirilmisti. Hemen fotografini cekip magazaya Facebook'tan mesaj attim. Yanit gelmeyince onlari aradim ve baska bir cift indirimli ayakkabiyla degistirmeyi reddettiler. Simdi 60 dolarlik, kirik bir cift striptizci topuklu ayakkabiyla sikisip kaldim.
Daha once, baska bir yetiskin butigi bana ayni markadan bir cift ayakkabi satmisti ve bu ayakkabi ilk vardiyamdan sonra kelimenin tam anlamiyla parcalanmisti, ancak onlara ne oldugunu anlattigimda saticilariyla iletisime gecip ayakkabilarimi degistirmek icin ellerinden geleni yaptilar.
Ne tur bir magaza oldugunu anliyorum ve iade politikalarinin bir nedenden dolayi yururlukte oldugunu anliyorum, ancak kullanilmis bir vibratoru iade etmiyorum veya daha yuksek degerli bir sey istemiyorum. Musteri hizmetleri acisindan yapilacak en dogru seyin magaza kredisi vermek veya para iadesi yapmak olacagini dusunuyorum. Yetiskin butiklerinde gardirobumuza o kadar cok para pompaliyoruz ki, bu para zaten Cindie'ye giderdi.

featured_reviews.review_id: Cindie's is always trying to give customers new experiences ... I can confirm w/out a doubt that the  Webster location is always VERY up to speed on all the products I have ever asked about.  No matter whether they are questions or comparisons or recommendations, the staff has always, at the very least, a helpful answer to guide your shopping selection.  They seem to be well versed w/the inventory, well beyond anything I may have known or even thought to ask. Even more importantly, they ALWAYS make you feel comfortable when sometimes the convo/question may be of a personal nature, or perhaps too intimate to speak out loud ... but they speak about those delicate issues w/such ease, like we're just having a normal convo & of course this creates a more positive environment & the communication begins to feel almost normal.  It's a relief to know that I can shop there w/no level of uncomfortable or awkwardness.  They are very good w/their choice of words & show no surprising reactions to anything, so I have never felt embarrassed for not knowing about "whatever" we're speaking about.  I'm just very grateful that Webster is my store because it is a pleasure doing business w/the staff there.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Cindie's her zaman musterilerine yeni deneyimler sunmaya calisiyor... Webster lokasyonunun simdiye kadar sordugum tum urunler konusunda her zaman COK guncel oldugunu supheye yer birakmayacak sekilde dogrulayabilirim. Sorular, karsilastirmalar veya tavsiyeler olsun, personel her zaman en azindan alisveris seciminize rehberlik edecek yararli bir yanita sahiptir. Envanter konusunda bilgili gorunuyorlar, bildigim ve hatta sormayi dusundugum her seyin cok otesinde. Daha da onemlisi, bazen gorusme/soru kisisel nitelikte oldugunda ya da yuksek sesle konusmak icin cok samimi oldugunda HER ZAMAN kendinizi rahat hissetmenizi saglarlar... ama bu hassas konular hakkinda sanki daha yeni yasiyormusuz gibi kolaylikla konusurlar. normal bir konvo ve tabii ki bu daha olumlu bir ortam yaratir ve iletisim neredeyse normalmis gibi gelmeye baslar. Orada hicbir duzeyde rahatsizlik veya gariplik olmadan alisveris yapabilecegimi bilmek beni rahatlatiyor. Kelime secimlerinde cok iyiler ve hicbir seye sasirtici tepkiler vermiyorlar, bu yuzden "her ne" hakkinda konustugumuzu bilmedigim icin hic utanmadim. Webster benim magazam oldugu icin cok minnettarim cunku oradaki personelle is yapmak bir zevk.

It was nice to have a an assistant that was interested in my needs and was wiling to take the time and the effort to make sure that I found what was right for me.  Kimmie, you were awesome.
featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Az once alisveris yapmak icin magazaniza geldim. Kimmie muhtesemdi. Beni cok rahatlatti ve satin alma islemimde cok yardimci oldu. Ihtiyacim olan dogru maddeleri bulmak icin hangi sorulari soracagini ve bilgiyi nasil isleyecegini biliyordu. Ihtiyaclarimla ilgilenen ve benim icin dogru olani buldugumdan emin olmak icin zaman ve caba harcamaya istekli bir asistanin olmasi guzeldi. Kimmie, harikaydin.
